data.description: Gorgeous ! Home Price reduced  with beautiful updates! Large, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with 2 living & 2 dining areas. Hardwood & tile flooring, split bedroom & open floor plan! Corner fireplace with cast stone hearth & gas log starter, master bathroom with dual sinks, garden tub, separate shower & his & her closets, modern wall treatments, eat-in & built-in kitchen with farm sink, skylight & tile backsplash, wood fence, 2 car garage, porch, patio & so much more! This home has a great pool in its  Hoa the home is close to private schools charter schools hospitals shopping and more! Make this stunner your dream home now!  Welcome home!
